Ray Barrett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ray_Barrett 0 Raymond Charles Barrett (2 May 1927 – 8 September 2009) was an Australian actor. During the 1960s, he was a leading actor on British television, where he was best known for his appearances in The Troubleshooters (1965–71). From the 1970s, he appeared in lead and character roles in a number of Australian films and TV series. Raymond_Charles_Barrett ( 2_May_1927 – 8_September_2009 ) was an_Australian_actor .
